OL,3,CAndrew investigation expands to
OL,4,Calleged misconduct at Royal Ascot,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FOfficers investigating Andrew
OL,8,FMountbatten-Windsor are reportedly
OL,9,Flooking into an allegation that he
OL,10,Fbehaved inappropriately towards a
OL,11,Fwoman at Royal Ascot.
OL,13,FThe alleged incident is said to have
OL,14,Fhappened at the racing event in
OL,15,FBerkshire in 2002, The Sunday Times
OL,16,Fhas reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
