OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779649870
OL,3,CAndrew investigation expands to
OL,4,Calleged misconduct at Royal Ascot,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FRoyal Ascot is a cornerstone of the
OL,8,Froyal family's summer calendar, and
OL,9,FQueen Elizabeth II was also at the
OL,10,Fevent in 2002, the year of her Golden
OL,11,FJubilee.
OL,13,FThe Sunday Times said it is not clear
OL,14,Fwhether the claim about alleged
OL,15,Finappropriate behaviour by Andrew was
OL,16,Freported to officers at the time or
OL,17,Fmore recently.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
