OL,3,CAndrew investigation expands to
OL,4,Calleged misconduct at Royal Ascot,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FA Thames Valley Police (TVP)
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "We cannot go into
OL,9,Fspecifics of the investigation, but we
OL,10,Fare following all reasonable lines of
OL,11,Finquiry."
OL,13,FThe force, which covers Windsor and
OL,14,FAscot in Berkshire, is continuing its
OL,15,Finvestigation into the former duke,
OL,16,Fand on Friday, it was confirmed that
OL,17,Fthey will consider allegations of
OL,18,Fsexual misconduct in their inquiry
OL,19,Finto potential misconduct in public
OL,20,Foffice.
OL,26,@pD@TOUsD@IO]
