CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779649870
OL,3,CAndrew investigation expands to
OL,4,Calleged misconduct at Royal Ascot,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FHe has denied any wrongdoing over his
OL,8,Flinks to the convicted sex offender.
OL,10,FTVP's major investigation is expected
OL,11,Fto be lengthy and will face obstacles,
OL,12,Fincluding trying to prove whether
OL,13,FAndrew held a public office at the
OL,14,Ftime of the allegations, something
OL,15,Fthat is not clearly legally defined.
OL,17,FHowever, it is understood that if this
OL,18,Fwere found not to be the case, the
OL,19,Fforce would continue investigating any
OL,20,Fevidence of other, separate offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
