OL,3,CAndrew investigation expands to
OL,4,Calleged misconduct at Royal Ascot,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FAndrew was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmisconduct in public office on
OL,9,FFebruary 19 and interviewed under
OL,10,Fcaution before being released under
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FSearches were also carried out at his
OL,19,Fformer homes in Windsor and Norfolk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
