OL,3,CAndrew investigation expands to
OL,4,Calleged misconduct at Royal Ascot,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FDetectives are understood to be
OL,8,Fworking through the evidence recovered
OL,9,Fduring the operation.
OL,11,FThey have also made a formal request
OL,12,Fto the United States Department of
OL,13,FJustice for the original versions of
OL,14,Fthe Epstein files, but have not yet
OL,15,Freceived any information.
OL,17,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,18,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,19,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,20,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
